            "id": "https://blog.lkhsss.cn/Linux/Raspberry-Pi-OS/%E6%A0%91%E8%8E%93%E6%B4%BE%EF%BC%9A%E4%BC%98%E9%9B%85%E5%9C%B0%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9swap%E5%88%86%E5%8C%BA%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%8F/",
            "url": "https://blog.lkhsss.cn/Linux/Raspberry-Pi-OS/%E6%A0%91%E8%8E%93%E6%B4%BE%EF%BC%9A%E4%BC%98%E9%9B%85%E5%9C%B0%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9swap%E5%88%86%E5%8C%BA%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%8F/",
            "title": "树莓派：优雅地修改swap分区大小",
            "date_published": "2024-04-14T00:53:38.000Z",
            "content_html": "<p>Raspberry Pi OS默认的swap分区为100MiB，这对于我买的sd卡来说这明显太小了。这时就可以用树莓派的配置文件来优雅地修改swap分区，而不用创建swap文件和使用奇淫巧计。</p>\n<h2 id=\"修改swap分区配置\">修改swap分区配置</h2>\n<p>配置文件地址：<code>/etc/dphys-swapfile</code><br>\n选择使用合你喜欢的方式编辑文本就行，但是要root权限。<br>\n比如：</p>\n<figure><div class=\"code-wrapper\"><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">sudo nano &#x2F;etc&#x2F;dphys-swapfile</code></pre></div></figure>\n<p>找到<code>CONF_SWAPSIZE</code>这一行，将后面的数字改为你想调整的大小，单位是MiB。(1GiB=1024MiB)</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>经过尝试，目前修改的最大swap分区大小为4048MiB</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>而<code>CONF_MAXSWAP</code>参数则用来设置最大大小，这个值应比<code>CONF_SWAPSIZE</code>大</p>\n<h2 id=\"重启swap服务\">重启swap服务</h2>\n<figure><div class=\"code-wrapper\"><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">sudo &#x2F;etc&#x2F;init.d&#x2F;dphys-swapfile restart</code></pre></div></figure>\n<p>重启完后可以使用<code>free -h</code>查看swap分区大小。</p>\n",
            "tags": [
                "树莓派"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "https://blog.lkhsss.cn/Linux/Kali/kali-%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%E6%BA%90-%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6%E6%BA%90/",
            "url": "https://blog.lkhsss.cn/Linux/Kali/kali-%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%E6%BA%90-%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6%E6%BA%90/",
            "title": "Kali 更新源/软件源",
            "date_published": "2023-02-04T12:05:16.000Z",
            "content_html": "<p>源文件位置：<code>/etc/apt/sources.list</code></p>\n<p>直接键入<code>sudo vim /etc/apt/sources.list</code>即可开始编辑</p>\n<h2 id=\"清华源\">清华源</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/kali/\">清华大学开源软件镜像站</a></p>\n<figure><div class=\"code-wrapper\"><pre class=\"line-numbers language-text\" data-language=\"text\"><code class=\"language-text\">deb http:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn&#x2F;kali kali-rolling main contrib non-free\ndeb-src https:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn&#x2F;kali kali-rolling main contrib non-free</code></pre></div></figure>\n<h2 id=\"阿里源\">阿里源</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://developer.aliyun.com/mirror/kali\">阿里巴巴开源镜像站</a></p>\n<figure><div class=\"code-wrapper\"><pre class=\"line-numbers language-text\" data-language=\"text\"><code class=\"language-text\">deb http:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirrors.aliyun.com&#x2F;kali kali-rolling main non-free contrib\ndeb-src http:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirrors.aliyun.com&#x2F;kali kali-rolling main non-free contrib</code></pre></div></figure>\n<h2 id=\"中科大源\">中科大源</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://mirrors.ustc.edu.cn/kali\">USTC Open Source Software Mirror</a></p>\n<figure><div class=\"code-wrapper\"><pre class=\"line-numbers language-text\" data-language=\"text\"><code class=\"language-text\">deb http:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirrors.ustc.edu.cn&#x2F;kali kali-rolling main non-free contrib\ndeb-src http:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirrors.ustc.edu.cn&#x2F;kali kali-rolling main non-free contrib</code></pre></div></figure>\n<h2 id=\"网易源\">网易源</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://mirrors.163.com/debian/\">网易开源镜像站</a></p>\n<figure><div class=\"code-wrapper\"><pre class=\"line-numbers language-text\" data-language=\"text\"><code class=\"language-text\">deb http:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirrors.163.com&#x2F;debian wheezy main non-free contrib\ndeb-src http:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirrors.163.com&#x2F;debian wheezy main non-free contrib\ndeb http:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirrors.163.com&#x2F;debian wheezy-proposed-updates main non-free contrib\ndeb-src http:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirrors.163.com&#x2F;debian wheezy-proposed-updates main non-free contrib\ndeb-src http:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirrors.163.com&#x2F;debian-security wheezy&#x2F;updates main non-free contrib</code></pre></div></figure>\n<h2 id=\"东软源\">东软源</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://mirrors.neusoft.edu.cn/kali/\">大连东软信息学院开源镜像站</a></p>\n<figure><div class=\"code-wrapper\"><pre class=\"line-numbers language-text\" data-language=\"text\"><code class=\"language-text\">deb http:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirrors.neusoft.edu.cn&#x2F;kali kali-rolling&#x2F;main non-free contrib\ndeb-src http:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirrors.neusoft.edu.cn&#x2F;kali kali-rolling&#x2F;main non-free contrib</code></pre></div></figure>\n<h2 id=\"官方源\">官方源</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://http.kali.org/kali/\">kali Linux | Penetration Testing Distribution</a></p>\n<figure><div class=\"code-wrapper\"><pre class=\"line-numbers language-text\" data-language=\"text\"><code class=\"language-text\">deb http:&#x2F;&#x2F;http.kali.org&#x2F;kali kali-rolling main non-free contrib\ndeb-src http:&#x2F;&#x2F;http.kali.org&#x2F;kali kali-rolling main non-free contrib</code></pre></div></figure>\n<h2 id=\"汇总\">汇总</h2>\n<figure><div class=\"code-wrapper\"><pre class=\"line-numbers language-text\" data-language=\"text\"><code class=\"language-text\">#清华大学\ndeb http:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn&#x2F;kali kali-rolling main contrib non-free\ndeb-src https:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn&#x2F;kali kali-rolling main contrib non-free\n#中科大\ndeb http:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirrors.ustc.edu.cn&#x2F;kali kali-rolling main non-free contrib\ndeb-src http:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirrors.ustc.edu.cn&#x2F;kali kali-rolling main non-free contrib\n#阿里云\ndeb http:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirrors.aliyun.com&#x2F;kali kali-rolling main non-free contrib\ndeb-src http:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirrors.aliyun.com&#x2F;kali kali-rolling main non-free contrib\n#163\ndeb http:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirrors.163.com&#x2F;debian wheezy main non-free contrib\ndeb-src http:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirrors.163.com&#x2F;debian wheezy main non-free contrib\ndeb http:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirrors.163.com&#x2F;debian wheezy-proposed-updates main non-free contrib\ndeb-src http:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirrors.163.com&#x2F;debian wheezy-proposed-updates main non-free contrib\ndeb-src http:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirrors.163.com&#x2F;debian-security wheezy&#x2F;updates main non-free contrib\n#东软大学\ndeb http:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirrors.neusoft.edu.cn&#x2F;kali kali-rolling&#x2F;main non-free contrib\ndeb-src http:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirrors.neusoft.edu.cn&#x2F;kali kali-rolling&#x2F;main non-free contrib\n#官方源\ndeb http:&#x2F;&#x2F;http.kali.org&#x2F;kali kali-rolling main non-free contrib\ndeb-src http:&#x2F;&#x2F;http.kali.org&#x2F;kali kali-rolling main non-free contrib</code></pre></div></figure>",
            "tags": [
                "Linux",
                "Kali"
            ]
